# Web3 Integration

The application integrates with blockchain technologies for authentication and functionality.

## Wallet Integration
- [lib/wallet.ts](mdc:lib/wallet.ts): Wallet utilities
- Uses RainbowKit for wallet connection
- Supports wagmi for Ethereum interactions
- Supports Solana via @solana/web3.js

## Authentication
- Privy authentication used for web3 login
- Implements JWT-based session management
- Protects routes with authentication middleware

## Blockchain Interactions
- Ethereum interactions via viem and wagmi
- Solana interactions via @solana/web3.js
- SPL token interactions via @solana/spl-token

## Providers
- Configures web3 providers in app layouts
- Handles wallet connection state
- Manages blockchain network detection and switching
